  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, multicenter, non-comparative, observational program to describe prevalence of
      depressive symptoms in a variety of neurological disorders and effects of Fevarin® on the
      severity of anxiety and depression, sleep state, and cognitive function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
